              <biblScope>LXXV 60–61, n. 4</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><author>Klima</author>, <ref
                type="bibl" target="#ref_Arch._Or."/>
              <biblScope>1958 XXVI 610</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><author>Benveniste</author>.
